    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artists who specialize in painting inanimate objects such as bowls of fruit, bottles, and flowers, which are often arranged in an aesthetic composition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
